> > >         Version: $__KERNELRELEASE
> > > -       Release: $(cat .version 2>/dev/null || echo 1)
> > > +       Release: $(init/build-version)
> >
> >
> > Ditto.
> >
> >           Release: $($srctree/init/build-version)
> 
> 
> 
> No, mkspec needs no change because binrpm-pkg builds the kernel
